title: 23 - Yannis Pappas
itunes:title: 23 - Yannis Pappas
description: Yannis Pappas. Brooklyn native. Raconteur. Co-host of the History Hyenas podcast. Lover of baseball caps. Blows your mind, steals your heart, sticks your theories about Brooklyn up your butt. All while reminding you how important proposals are. Here are five words about this episode: Yankees will last the longest.
